{"tid":2233111,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支持Trump連任, 不必硬撐Trump的所有行為.","createTime":"2020-10-07T01:30:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T13:23:05.000Z","uid":134071,"like":90,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"dae36d50b00b84d773211cd75cdcc512eaaf3cc0","tid":2233111,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T01:30:12.000Z","msg":"其實支持Donald Trump連任,&nbsp;理由可以好簡單:&nbsp;Trump團隊支持香港, 出力抗共.<br />\n<br />\n反而,&nbsp;唔駛因此硬撐Trump的所有行為. 見到某啲有關Trump既負面新聞,&nbsp;唔需要硬撐, 頂多無視就得.<br />\n<br />\n如果嘗試每樣野都硬撐Trump,&nbsp;老實講,&nbsp;可能影響自己既情緒.<br />\n反之, 對香港人黎講,&nbsp;Trump團隊肯表態支持香港,&nbsp;就係在心中樂見佢連任既充分理由.<br />\n<br />\n波多黎各總督的說法, 可以給予大家參考.<br />\n<br />\n<em>波多黎各總督: <strong>無人係完美, 但我支持Donald Trump連任, 因為Donald Trump可代表波多黎各人.</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newsweek.com/puerto-rico-governor-endorses-trump-says-he-represents-puerto-ricans-nobody-perfect-1536870\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Fpuerto-rico-governor-endorses-trump-says-he-represents-puerto-ricans-nobody-perfect-1536870&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmUPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=6c49f65b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newsweek.com/puerto-rico-governor-endorses-trump-says-he-represents-puerto-ricans-nobody-perfect-1536870</a><br />\n<br />\nPuerto Rico Governor Endorses Trump, Says He Represents Puerto Ricans: 'Nobody Is Perfect'<br />\nBy Christina Zhao On 10/6/20 at 7:23 PM EDT"},{"pid":"43bb4afa3b3537b4f672b6e59d6891f62200556b","tid":2233111,"uid":164128,"like":18,"dislike":14,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T01:31:26.000Z","msg":"too many brain-dead trumptards"},{"pid":"10fb3a93ec543352ee0faea98061a76a8093e59d","tid":2233111,"uid":49018,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T01:31:54.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"2de7d1ffdc5dabddbbe44731b227d83ffcae2c6b","tid":2233111,"uid":134071,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"43bb4afa3b3537b4f672b6e59d6891f62200556b","tid":2233111,"uid":164128,"like":18,"dislike":14,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T01:31:26.000Z","msg":"too many brain-dead trumptards"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T01:34:01.000Z","msg":"諗咁多野,&nbsp;只係令到自己辛苦.&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實,&nbsp; Trump團隊肯見香港抗爭者,&nbsp;Biden團隊拒見,&nbsp;已經係好理由支持Donald Trump連任.... 唔駛太花心力諗其他野.<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a92ebb8b2652f59ab464a33adceb5e55ac8d2f3","tid":2233111,"uid":134071,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"10fb3a93ec543352ee0faea98061a76a8093e59d","tid":2233111,"uid":49018,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T01:31:54.000Z","msg":"真"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T01:35:40.000Z","msg":"王丹說法都可供大家參考.&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=10157635030973027&amp;id=105759983026\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpermalink.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10157635030973027%26id%3D105759983026&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmUPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=3807665d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=10157635030973027&amp;id=105759983026</a><br />\n<br />\n王丹网站 Wang Dan's Page<br />\n4 天 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n我表態支持川普連任，只有一個理由，就是他的團隊對中共的政策，方向正確。<br />\n<br />\n一堆人跳出來反對我，說川普的行事風格和所作所為，會毀掉美國的民主自由。<br />\n<br />\n我也覺得川普的言行對美國的民主是威脅，但現在，對民主自由最大的威脅，不是川普，而是中共。而川普的政府團隊，比拜登的政府團隊，對中共的認識更清醒，也更有可能打擊到中共。<br />\n<br />\n我不是那麼自私的人，好像一切考量都是從我們反共人士的利益出發。不是的。我的出發點很清楚：<br />\n<br />\n不消滅中共，受害的不僅是我們，而是全世界，也包括美國。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>兩害相權取其輕，這個道理，很複雜嗎？<br />\n<br />\n這就是儘管我很不喜歡川普這個人，但是我支持川普連任的原因。</strong>"},{"pid":"263e9daa67eaeeeb887915d81b85211cc16d2dca","tid":2233111,"uid":55089,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T01:36:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c301ef7650582c75c12c07bee93592be777fd15","tid":2233111,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"263e9daa67eaeeeb887915d81b85211cc16d2dca","tid":2233111,"uid":55089,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T01:36:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T01:37:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b564e0fa6d91a2888147bd7ea9dfd9ab6a64477e","tid":2233111,"uid":52760,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T01:38:21.000Z","msg":"Trump有反共決心<br />\n我只會理依點<br />\n其他都與我無關"},{"pid":"042413f27356f8171de4a44457f919c712c43d63","tid":2233111,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b564e0fa6d91a2888147bd7ea9dfd9ab6a64477e","tid":2233111,"uid":52760,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T01:38:21.000Z","msg":"Trump有反共決心<br />\n我只會理依點<br />\n其他都與我無關"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T01:38:39.000Z","msg":"態度正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3493a903ef330345f7be46ff5776d2b159194f14","tid":2233111,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T01:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e876121d9ab6bf60a22fe1e30294e4fd8d123435","tid":2233111,"uid":134071,"like